                     <interp inst="t18291029-86-off466" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291029-86-off466" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291029-86-cd467" type="crimeDate">17th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-86-off466 t18291029-86-cd467"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-86-off471 t18291029-86-cd467"></join>, 6 veils, value 1l. 3s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
